                                        izračun. Preverili bomo razpoložljivost dvoran in vam poslali ponudbo naslednji
                                        delovni dan po prejemu. Oddano povpraševanje še ne pomeni rezervacije prostora.<br/><br/>
                                        S spoštovanjem,
                                        <br/><br/>
                                        Ljubljanski grad
                                    </p>
                                    <%} else {%>
                                    <p style="font-family: Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans,Lucida Sans Unicode,Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;">
                                        Dear Sir or Madam,<br/><br/>
                                        Thank you for your inquiry. A provisional calculation of the cost has been sent to your email address. We will check the availability of the halls and send you an offer on the next business day after receipt of your inquiry. The submitted inquiry does not mean that the space has been reserved.<br/><br/>
                                        Yours sincerely,
                                        <br/><br/>
                                        Ljubljana Castle

                                    </p>
                                    <% } %>
                                    <br/>
                                    <br/>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>


                                    <td style="color:#333; font-family: Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans,Lucida Sans Unicode,Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif; line-height:28px; font-size:16px;padding-bottom:20px;font-weight:bold;">
                                        <% if(data.language == 'sl-SI'){%>
                                        Podatki o naročniku:
                                        <%} else {%>
                                        Information about the order:
                                        <% } %>
                                        <ul style="list-style: none; font-weight: normal; padding: 0;">
                                            <li><%- data.inquiry.name %></li>
                                            <li><%- data.inquiry.contactName %></li>
                                            <li><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #333"
                                                   href="mailto:<%- data.inquiry.email %>"><%- data.inquiry.email %></a>
                                            </li>
                                            <% if(data.inquiry.phone) { %>
                                            <li><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #333"
                                                   href="tel:<%- data.inquiry.phone %>"><%- data.inquiry.phone %></a>
                                                <% } %>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>


                                    <td style="color:#333; text-align: right; vertical-align: top; font-family: Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans,Lucida Sans Unicode,Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif; line-height:28px; font-size:16px;padding-bottom:20px;font-weight:bold;">
                                        &nbsp;
                                        <ul style="list-style: none; font-weight: normal; padding: 0;">
                                            <li><%- data.hall.name[data.language] %></li>
                                            <% if(data.price) { %>
                                            <li>Cena <b><%- data.price %> €</b> brez DDV</li>
                                            <% } %>
                                            <li><%- data.niceDate %><%- (data.startTime ? ', ' + data.startTime.hour + ':' + data.startTime.minute : '')+(data.endTime ? '-' + data.endTime.hour + ':' + data.endTime.minute : '') %>
